Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:39.86,tari--TITLE1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,564)\fad(500,0)}亦白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:39.86,tari--TITLE1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(609,639)\fad(500,0)}亦红
